        <p>
            Fake Account Detection is an advanced web-based platform designed to help users identify fraudulent social media accounts. With the increasing number of fake profiles on social media, users often fall victim to scams, misinformation, and identity theft. Our website uses data-driven analysis and intelligent algorithms to differentiate between real and fake accounts. By evaluating profile engagement, account activity, and behavioral patterns, we provide users with a seamless way to verify the authenticity of accounts, ensuring a safer online experience.
        
